# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# pain-metabolism.form — pain with provenance: the felt event names its
# tissue, and what it names is metabolized
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# The ask (2026-06-11): weave the learning machinery into cell pain
# sensing so we know which recipes and cells were involved in the pain,
# and how we can learn from it.
#
# The body already FEELS in scattered nerves — ec-reflex-pain (the cost
# of repeating a carrier choice the body has outgrown), novelty.fk
# (surprise below the recognition floor), drift-detect (predicted ≠
# actual), anomaly-band (outside the band), body-state (the counts),
# and the witness's organ silences at pulse/now. What was missing is
# the pathway from "it hurts" to "we know which tissue, and we
# learned." That pathway is now one module of thin tissue over the
# proven learning spine:
#
#   feel      pn-felt — the event as a field: magnitude at the site
#   trace     the walk's involvement graph as (touched toucher strength)
#             edge data — pn-touch builds rows in call order; the SAME
#             (i j w) shape every gather already reads
#   name      pn-involved = clc-spread over the trace: strongest-path
#             involvement per cell, with the untouched provably ZERO —
#             "which recipes and cells were involved" is a computed
#             field, never a guess. pn-credit ranks the edges;
#             pn-hottest names the one that carried the most.
#             pn-cone (over mtb-reverse) is the predictive direction:
#             who will feel THIS cell when it fails.
#   learn     four metabolic moves, each proven:
#             · release — pn-release-at weakens the hottest edge;
#               the re-felt walk illuminates strictly less (healing
#               is measured, not hoped)
#             · research — the failing samples go to ls-research and
#               the style-space loop crowns a replacement row (pain
#               drives the auto-ml lane; champion-challenger is the
#               promotion gate when the replacement must earn a route)
#             · remember — the involvement field, r6-binned, IS the
#               pain's receipt; nearest-shape recalls a recurring pain
#               ("felt-before"), and novelty.fk keeps a genuinely new
#               pain NEW — interned, never force-matched
#             · triage — novel pain first, then the loudest of the
#               known: curiosity turned toward what hurts
#
# SHIPPED: form/form-stdlib/pain-metabolism.fk +
# tests/pain-metabolism-band.fk → 1023 (10 claims), three-way
# (Go/Rust/TS), composing geometric-learning + cognitive-light-cone +
# metabolic-learning + nearest-shape/learning-arc + novelty +
# learning-style-space.
#
# The band's walk: route → recipe-A → {cell-x, cell-y}, with recipe-B
# and cell-z untouched. Pain 8 at the route. Involvement [8 8 4 2 0 0]
# — exact; the untouched branch exactly zero; cell-x's failure
# provably reaches the route while cell-y's never reaches cell-z;
# releasing the hottest edge halves everything downstream; the second
# identical pain recalls its receipt; a different pain shares zero
# bins and is honestly novel; the hurting recipe's failing samples
# crown the alternative through ls-research; the novel event triages
# first.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The production path (named, walked as asks arrive)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# The trace rows are the lift point: the kernel already emits walk
# evidence — the framebuffer/trace JSON shows arm dispatch (including
# Form category) per request, and X-Form-Router names the carrier.
# Lifting a real request's dispatch trace into pn-touch rows gives
# pn-involved over PRODUCTION tissue: a 500, a silence, or a reflex-
# pain event at a route illuminates the recipes and cells that walk
# touched, with strengths. The receipt store then accumulates the
# body's pain history as content-addressed shapes — recurring
# production pain recognized by shape across days, not log-grepping.
# Next stones when asked: trace-JSON → pn-touch lifting; receipts as
# substrate cells (BDomain ingest) so equivalence comes for free;
# wiring ec-reflex-pain events as pn-felt sources; the witness's
# organ silences as site seeds.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Kinship
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
#   metabolic-learning.form     the operator this module turns toward
#                               wounds: credit → gift/release, the
#                               satsang strategies over the gather
#   cognitive-light-cone.form   the cone is the involvement geometry;
#                               expressive vs receptive = "what did
#                               this pain touch" vs "who feels me"
#   learning-style-space.form   where the failing samples go — pain
#                               drives the research loop's curiosity
#   edge-categories.fk          ec-reflex-pain — the reflex-pain
#                               source this pathway metabolizes
#   body-state.fk               the count surface pain events feed
#   choice-receipt.fk           the discrete sibling of pain receipts
#   when-the-pressure-comes.form the human teaching underneath: what
#                               to do when shit happens, as recipes
